data.description: Cute as a button ranch located in Berkshire Meadows neighborhood in Suffolk. Cul-de-sac location, near neighborhood park. Open floorplan with family room, dining area, kitchen and breakfast nook. 3 good sized bedrooms and 2 full baths including owner's suite with 2 closets. Neutral paint throughout and many updates. Fenced yard in back. Great location - near hospital, interstate, bases, Downtown, shopping and restaurants. This is a great house for sure. Don't miss it!
